Package foldocparser

Provides parsing services for converting a FOLDOC-like dictionary into an ontology

See:
          Description

Class Summary
KV A key, value pair
Normalizer A class to provide on-the-fly normalization of graph node weights
Outputter A class providing static functions for the textual output of a fdg graph to RDF or DOT
Parse A command line wrapper for the Parser for FOLDOC-like dictionaries
Parser A Parser for a FOLDOC-ish dictionary.
Tester An obsolete generic tester
Token A Dictionary token, eventually kept with each link to represent tags.
When serialized, only the flags (a single integer) are kept.
Tokenizer Provides high-level tokenization of a textual source to provide Parser with construction tokens.
